It won't do anything at idle as it's not supposed to.

> considerable amount of suction when i put my finger
> over it.  How do i check the disributor vacume system?

There is not supposed to be any suction at idle, you might have the 
wrong hose hooked up.  The advance hose is supposed to hook up to your 
throttle body, not your manifold.

